@anotherkevin, in order to get around the freezing issue you will need metal or concrete vessels to hold your water 44 gallon drums for example. Also you might have  leaking gutter somewhere or another downspout that you aren&#8217;t aware of, because there is no way that you could be getting that little runoff from your roof unless your house is tiny!</p>
